FORP.Name: Forseti II
FORP.Message: This mighty keep serves as a grand battlefield, with plentiful weapons, and a good balance between open-area combat and architecture.  A good 2 player or more rumble.

GEFI.Name: Gefjon II
GEFI.Message: The spacious but intricate temple of Gefjon offers an excellent battleground for epic matches of skill and death-dealing.

RAGK.Name: Ragnarok II
RAGK.Message: Ragnarok's relatively small, enclosed deathdome offers close-quarter action, yet balances this with numerous cover areas and platforms.

LEMA.Name: Lemon Lender II
LEMA.Message: I do business in new, factory refurbished new, and used lemons.
